Jessie

If we move up the train,
car by car, we should get past it!”

Jessie
“You want an explanation?
OK!! Let me.”

Jessie
“This train's security system is
the old Shinra A system.”{PAUSE}“Once it identifies an illegal ID,
the system automatically locks down each car.”{PAUSE}“It'll stay locked until it gets to the station,
where Shinra guards will be waiting.”

Jessie
“But it's an old system, we can get past it.”{PAUSE}“If we move from car to car to the front,
we should be able to go on as planned.”

Jessie
“The second detection scan
should be coming up pretty soon.
Let's go to the next car!”

“It's my fault that we didn't
clear the ID scan.”{PAUSE}“I modified the ID card for
{Cloud} and that's
what made the sensors go off.”{PAUSE}“I did my best, but
it just didn't work.”

"I'll make a better one next time."
"I'll head back to the hideout first
and work on research and development.”
